long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is a download assistant, sending online video links to Kraken for download.
The desktop download software Kraken can be downloaded and installed from the official website: http://www.krakengine.com.

Features:
Supports sending and downloading MP3 video links;
Supports sending and downloading HLS video links;

Notes:
This extension is only suitable for sending and downloading video links using general playback technology, it does not download from a specific website;
This extension cannot send and download YouTube video links;
This extension cannot send and download encrypted video links;
This extension does not assume any legal responsibility for the media content you download, it is recommended that you ensure the copyright and permissions of the media before downloading.
